              "coded_information": [
                "MCPLT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two timing detectors based on microchannel",
                "plate were designed for determining the",
                "time-of-flight of fission fragments. The time",
                "resolution was determined with two MCP timing",
                "detectors to be 157ps (FWHM) for 241Am radiation",
                "source, implying that the intrinsic time resolution",
                "is about 110ps (FWHM) for a single timing detector."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The axial grid ionization chamber was used for",
                "determining the kinetic energy of fission fragments.",
                "The intrinsic energy resolution of it was measured to",
                "be about 0.5% for 80 MeV 63Cu particles."
              ]
            }
          ],
